        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2026 14:30:00 +0900</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Separate notification sounds for Done and Needs Input</li>
                    <li>8 fun built-in notification sounds (Finish!, Ding Dong, Magnificent, Brilliant, Hey Hey Hey, Excuse Me Human, Attention Please, Eora?!)</li>
                    <li>Custom sound support — drop .aiff files into ~/Library/Sounds/</li>
                    <li>macOS notifications and webhooks now work independently</li>
                    <li>Improved settings layout with grouped sections</li>
                    <li>Input field labels for webhook settings (Webhook URL, Bot Token, Chat ID)</li>
                    <li>Improved webhook setup guides</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
